Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.69,0:00:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}De ce povestesc dintr-odată despre asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.27,0:00:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Se presupunea că doar simulez un interviu cu Mernes ca să-l ajut cu abilitățile sale în ale comunicării...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai spus că vrei să distrugi umanitatea.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.23,0:02:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar asta nu e adevărat, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.94,0:02:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă gândeam că Shutina mă va întreba asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt surprins să văd că vine de la tine.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.61,0:02:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-ai spus să mă pun în locul lor și să încerc să-mi dau seama ce urmează să mă întrebe.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.81,0:02:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa că asta am făcut.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.94,0:02:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și așa mi-am dat seama.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.27,0:02:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu ai nevoie de noi. Ai putea distruge umanitatea de unul singur.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.86,0:02:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bună treabă! Dacă poți empatiza atât de bine, atunci ești deja un maestru în ale comunicării...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.48,0:03:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bun, dă-mi voie să-ți pregătesc diploma! Oare unde am pus-o?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.27,0:03:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, poftim, zece tichete de masă la Restaurantul Șobolanului! Felicitări!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu încerca să schimbi subiectul.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De ce nu ai distrus-o încă?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.73,0:03:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și eu mă întreb același lucru! Oare de ce nu am făcut-o?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.11,0:03:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu te face că nu știi!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, ai grijă!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu te deranjează?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.40,0:03:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai făcut tot posibilul ca să-i protejezi, iar ei doar s-au descotorosit de tine.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ți-ai riscat viața luptând împotriva noastră.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu le-ai dorit niciodată moartea?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.27,0:03:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu da.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.31,0:03:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-ai investigat trecutul, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.36,0:03:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, puțin. Știu că ești\N jumătate om, jumătate demon.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.90,0:04:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oamenilor le era frică de tine, \Nașa că părinții tăi te-au vândut ca sclav,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.61,0:04:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,iar după ce ai avut mai mulți stăpâni, ai ajuns în Breasla Asasinilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa este.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.56,0:04:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guild thought I'd be expendable,\Nthat I'd die taking out my first and only target.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for better or for worse...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,am fost un asasin destul de bun încât să supraviețuiesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cu toții...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,meritați să muriți!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I was more than supportive\Nof the Demon Army's invasion.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.15,0:04:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I so desperately wanted them\Nto finish off humanity once and for all.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've startling news! The castle gates have opened for us!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.65,0:04:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well. Do not let this chance escape us!\NAll troops, move in!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.15,0:05:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I raced ahead of their forces and\Nsecretly gave them my assistance.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.86,0:05:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.44,0:05:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fear not! We have not come to slaughter you!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our objective lies in the Capital, in Renailles!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.15,0:05:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will rebuild the town as we use it\Nas our new base of operations.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've also captured your corrupt mayor.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.19,0:05:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was so much food in his castle!\NLet's share it together!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.81,0:05:57.02,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Okay, line up! Don't worry, there's enough for everyone!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.52,0:05:58.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't we kill them? It was a waste of precious time.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.65,0:06:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite my doubts, I made contact with Echidna,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and joined the army under false pretenses.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we leave this town and proceed forward?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.48,0:06:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight, though, the populace is providing us\Nwith a grand welcome.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.36,0:06:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've liberated us and restored peace.\NWe can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.73,0:06:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think nothing of it.\NIt was a necessary part of our own plans.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.31,0:06:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is good! You should try this!\NDoes anyone want refills on juice?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is crazy! We're in the middle of an invasion,\Nhosting a grand feast?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.94,0:06:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand your frustration, but this, too,\Nis part of Queen Echidna's strategy.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.02,0:06:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non-stop fighting will lead to burned-out troops.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.65,0:06:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This creates the opportunity\Nfor them to refresh themselves
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.19,0:07:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and for her to speak one-on-one with\Nher subordinates, reigniting their motivation.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their motivation?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been working hard.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm honored that you've noticed!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.06,0:07:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our Queen is a strange one, isn't she?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.77,0:07:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I joined up, I thought the Army was\Nan evil force hell-bent on destroying humanity.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so did I...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why when they asked me to join, I said no!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.23,0:07:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are horrible humans, true,\Nbut that don't mean they all deserve to burn.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.11,0:07:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then I saw that this is who they really are.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.15,0:07:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, no man or woman who\Nloves good ale can be a villain!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.81,0:07:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mernes, why did you join the Demon Army?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.06,0:08:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell them I'd joined with\Nthe hopes of slaughtering humanity.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.81,0:08:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mernes, I'm glad to have you among us.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be needing your help again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.86,0:08:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once we have the Philosopher's Stone,\Nand the Demon World has become a paradise,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.94,0:08:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I invite you to join us there.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expect you'd like living somewhere peaceful and quiet.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Leaving already?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aww, I wanted to hang out with you though!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.69,0:08:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I need to, I'll take out Echidna and\Nlead the Demon Army myself to destroy humanity.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I became one of the Great Generals,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.86,0:08:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and half-heartedly helped lead its brilliant forces\Nthrough its successful campaign.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.36,0:08:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, successful until SOMEONE came along.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.81,0:08:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.65,0:09:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said that day?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've lost. Kill me.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.19,0:09:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't, then someday, I'll exterminate humanity.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.94,0:09:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. You're acting like you've never seen\Nanything cool in your whole life.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go out and see the world a little, man.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.31,0:09:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've done that, and I'm bored of it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.44,0:09:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This world sucks. Nothing in it is 'cool'.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.69,0:09:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because you've only seen it as an assassin.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.98,0:09:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The world looks different when you're seeing it\Non your own terms, not just for work.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if it's that easy...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like I'd know that, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.23,0:09:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, here's my advice for you right now:
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.86,0:10:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go seek out something in the world you've never seen.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you still want to die after that, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and if you do something evil, I'll kill you too.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.19,0:10:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.73,0:10:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You spouted off all those high-and-mighty words,\Nso why'd you decide to quit?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To destroy humanity? I know that's a lie.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.69,0:10:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care what happens to humanity.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you don't seem to have, the, uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hatred for mankind?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.36,0:10:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You've got something else going on.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.56,0:10:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Else, you wouldn't have said all that stuff to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.81,0:10:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.81,0:10:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They betrayed you. Normally people\Nget angry when they're betrayed.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get sad, you hate them, you truly start to hate them...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.81,0:10:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.56,0:11:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm learning way too many new things\Nabout these guys now that I've joined them.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.31,0:11:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prim and proper Shutina is a klutz\Nwho barely keeps herself afloat.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brainless wild child is a diligent, good kid.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now we've got Mernes.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:14.86,0:11:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The uncaring, unfeeling assassin\Nstruggles with teenage angst.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.40,0:11:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason he kept quiet after hearing my reasons for\Njoining wasn't that he didn't like me.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:26.56,0:11:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He heard how I'd been exiled by humanity\Nand felt for me from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:32.73,0:11:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, man, don't cry. Now I feel like it's my fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.90,0:11:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll listen, so just tell me!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.73,0:12:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, getting told "we don't need you" and\N"kill the hero" made me feel pretty shitty.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.69,0:12:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially since I've been defending\Nhumanity for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long...?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you what the world was like when I was born.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a long, long time ago...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I telling him this for?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:17.02,0:12:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the height of industrial civilization,\Nbefore magic came into common use.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The land was shaped a bit differently than it is now,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.27,0:12:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and where the Capital now stands,\Nthere stood the city of Tokyo...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We launched rockets into the sea of stars,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.56,0:12:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,encircled the earth with swarms of man-made satellites,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:41.69,0:12:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and an invisible, high-speed communication\Nnetwork connected the planet.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:46.48,0:12:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were tensions, but mostly peace,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:48.31,0:12:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and unlike our diverse world,\Nmine was made up of only humans.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.73,0:12:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, one day...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hole opened up in the middle of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.23,0:13:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From it came imps, dwarves, orcs,\Ngoblins, succubi and incubi...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All manner of demons we're well-acquainted with now.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.94,0:13:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, we just called them "demons".
Dialogue: 100,0:13:26.27,0:13:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Echidna, they were sick of the dark,\Nhorrific Demon World,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.90,0:13:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and came to the human world\Nseeking its warmth and light.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.86,0:13:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many tried to peacefully exist alongside humanity,\Nbut others opted for violence.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.86,0:13:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was humanity going to do?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fight back, of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:46.31,0:13:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What had started on an eastern island nation\Nspread around the world,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:49.98,0:13:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it wasn't long until there was a full-out world\Nwar on demon kind.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And sadly,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.65,0:13:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humans back then were as weak as they are now.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It took dozens of humans just to get rid of one demon.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need stronger weapons!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:05.61,0:14:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, an unstoppable weapon that can\Nprotect humanity from this demonic threat!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now is the time for humanity to join as one!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:15.94,0:14:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To kill a demon, we must create a demon ourselves.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The project is nearly complete.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.31,0:14:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've used the demon's own power\Nto forge twelve powerful weapons,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.19,0:14:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,living beings with limitless potential\Nto evolve, grow, and protect humanity.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Demonhart Series!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As of now,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:36.11,0:14:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,only one Demonhart survives.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's me.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a living weapon?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-what the hell does that mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:49.40,0:14:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the moment I was born, I was a hero.\NI knew no other way of life.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.40,0:15:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My orders were planted at inception:\NProtect humanity. Save the world.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:05.61,0:15:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All heroes grow old and die,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:08.77,0:15:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I was made to be extremely durable and long-lived.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:13.69,0:15:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other DH Series models fell in battle, one by one,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,leaving me as the only surviving hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'll put it this way.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.69,0:15:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd missed my chance to die.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:35.81,0:15:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even after the industrial world fell, and magic\Nreplaced machinery, I went on living.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:43.23,0:15:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened so long ago, I can barely remember it.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:47.40,0:15:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever war erupted, I was there to fight.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:52.06,0:15:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd grown too strong to die in battle.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:58.11,0:16:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity. Save the world.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.77,0:16:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were my orders,\Nbut were they the right things to do?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was I just keeping humanity dependent on me?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one could answer those questions.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like I'd know that, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:24.98,0:16:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't abandon my duty to protect the world.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the world pushed me aside just recently,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sure, I was a little sad to hear it.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:39.15,0:16:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't upset about it. In fact...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:51.06,0:16:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I WAS happy.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.11,0:16:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.65,0:17:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those warm words of "we don't need you"\Nand "let's kill him"...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.61,0:17:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...were the most meaningful words I'd ever heard.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.44,0:17:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It finally gave me a chance to quit heroing.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have to protect humanity.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:23.15,0:17:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next time humanity needs protection,\NI can just do whatever I want.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:28.56,0:17:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can be myself. Go see the parts of the world\NI want to see, on my own terms.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:35.90,0:17:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm spending my 'second' life doing\Nwhat I always wanted: joining the demons.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:42.48,0:17:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.31,0:17:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Echidna didn't just get up and\Ngo back to the demon world.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:45.98,0:17:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know her father, Demon King Cychreus?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.69,0:17:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand a single thing you've said.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.44,0:17:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wasted NO time going home.\NDidn't even get a chance to talk!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:55.11,0:17:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I said, hold on!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:57.94,0:18:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did I tell him all that?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You know how the saying goes,\Na good communicator is a good listener!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Once people know you're a good listener,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:05.90,0:18:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted someone to hear my story.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.77,0:18:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}they'll start coming to you, asking to vent or to get some advice.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.27,0:18:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't hold it in. Talk it out, yeah?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.65,0:18:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assumed some good listener out there\Nwould ask me about it someday.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knew it'd end up being you.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:26.27,0:18:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not making sense.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.02,0:18:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potrivit legendei, invazia Lordului Demon Cychreus a fost acum o mie de ani!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:32.61,0:18:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da. Și potrivit legendei, \Nun „misterios înțelept” a salvat lumea.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.69,0:18:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu am fost acela.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce? Atunci, câți ani ai?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu, mai bine spus...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce ești tu, mai exact?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.31,0:18:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just an ex-hero they built to be\Na bit tougher than the rest.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cât despre câți ani am... Nu am idee.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sincer să fiu, m-am oprit din numărat când am trecut de o mie.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:55.81,0:18:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O mie?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:57.36,0:19:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, though, you live this long, you meet a lot of people.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.02,0:19:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You meet one person you want to protect with your life,\Nthen another you want to see dead.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So believe me when I say this.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys are a good lot.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:14.73,0:19:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Echidna and the Great Guardians\Nare all big goofballs, but they're good people.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:18.36,0:19:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good enough to make me want\Nto work my butt off for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goofballs?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.56,0:19:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci nu vă faceți griji. Voi face rost de Piatra Filosofală pentru voi.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:33.69,0:19:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă voi asigura că vă veți găsi fericirea.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vai...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:42.94,0:19:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't get it. And you're not going\Nto explain any further, are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.44,0:19:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get around to it.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:49.61,0:19:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, I hadn't planned on telling you all this, either.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:53.27,0:19:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci, de ce mi-ai spus?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.77,0:19:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you looked serious, I guess.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd felt this since that moment at the lake.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:05.23,0:20:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not the best talker, but he's got the\None thing that makes you a good communicator:
Dialogue: 100,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turn me into a master communicator.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O motivație puternică.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:17.69,0:20:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That genuine desire is the most\Nimportant part of communicating well.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:24.44,0:20:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might be blunt and awkward,\Nbut I could tell you really wanted to hear me out.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't stop myself\Nfrom telling you everything.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:36.81,0:20:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just need to be genuine and thoughtful,\Njust like you are now.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.77,0:20:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll do great in your interviews. I know\Nyou'll be able to get the applicants to open up.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:51.06,0:20:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm done, and I'm tired. I'm going to pass out here.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.19,0:20:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on, you've got your own room!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we've got another long day in the cafeteria\Ntomorrow!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:59.31,0:21:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noapte bună.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:00.31,0:21:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, Mernes! Don't pass out on me!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.52,0:21:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never change, though, do you?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:40.40,0:21:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might be able to mediate.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:31.86,0:23:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, tată...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:06.02,Caption,,0,0,0,,Episodul 6: Eroul își spune povestea de viață
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.06,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,Data viitoare
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.06,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,Un războinic bun nu înseamnă și un șef bun
